    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Avatar of the War Spirit (Rank 5, Legendary)</p><p>Cost: 4 Gnosis  </p><p>Activation: Action  </p><p>Duration: 1 minute</p><p>You fully embody the ancient war-spirits of the Garou, becoming a living engine of destruction.</p><p>For the duration:</p><p>• You have advantage on all attack rolls.</p><p>• You have resistance to all damage.</p><p>• Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack, you deal an additional 2d10 damage.</p><p>Aftereffects:</p><p>• Your Rage immediately ends when the effect ends.</p><p>• You gain 2 levels of exhaustion.</p><p>• This gift cannot be used again until the next dawn.</p><p></p>",
